posting_body: ['Apartments For Rent in Renton, Washington', 'Springbrook has spacious one and two bedroom apartments, and two bedroom, and three bedroom town homes.', 'Our community offers a theater room, fitness center, tanning bed, seasonal outdoor pool, and a year round hot tub.', 'With shopping, restaurants, and entertainment just minutes down the road you will sure love to call Springbrook home.', 'Call Now:', 'show contact info', 'x 70', 'OR Text', '70', 'to', 'show contact info', 'to chat!', 'Want more info?', 'See the link below:', '<URL>', 'This is a 1 Bedroom, 1 Bath, approximately 795-854 Sq.', 'Ft.', 'Features', '- Wood burning fireplace', '- So come on down to Springbrook Apartments and Townhomes and have a tour, you wont want to miss calling this place home!', '- Nine foot ceilings', '- Laminate maple cabinets', '- Plank flooring - in select homes', '- Fully equipped kitchen', '- And so much more.', '- Walk in closets', '- Each of our homes include', '- Entertaining size deck or patio', '- Stainless appliances - in select homes', '- Full size washer and dryer', '- Lots of extra closet space', '- Ceramic tile entry way', 'Community Amenities', '- Rentable Carports', '- Seasonal outdoor pool', '- Attached garages - in select townhomes', '- Rentable Detached Garages', '- Business Center', '- Package Concierge', '- Year Round Spa', '- Fitness Center', '- Tanning Bed', '- Theatre room', 'Pet Policy', 'We accept cats and dogs as long as they are not part of our breed restrictions list.', 'There is no weight limit.', 'There is a maximum of 2 pets per home.', 'Call for information on applicable deposits and fees.', 'Income Requirements:', 'A minimum of 2.8 times the rental rate is required for all homes.', 'Office Hours', 'Monday-Friday: 9:00AM-6:00PM', 'Saturday: 10:00AM-5:00PM', 'Springbrook', '5301 Talbot Road S , Renton, WA, 98055', 'We do not accept Comprehensive Reusable Tenant Screening Reports as defined by and pursuant to RCW 59.18.', 'dTo7Ide7sMJ']
